canNotAddModules(address[]).return: True if all modules can be added, false otherwise

addModule(address).notice: Add module functions. Overriding functions is not allowed. To replace modules use ReplaceModule function.

removeModule(address).notice: to disable module - set all its functions implementation to address(0)

replaceModule(address,address).notice: Replace module - remove the previous, add the new one
